node.text:
The Morning.
.
.
My new risograph comic “Morning” is now available, link in my bio!
.
Beautifully printed by @risolve , “Morning” is a 36 page 9.75” x 7.5” comic.  Printed in blue, bubblegum, and sunflower, this comic really pops in the light. 
.
Thank you to everyone who has bought a copy, I am really excited to share this book with you all. I spent a long time on this book and I think its one of the more personal stories I’ve ever told. So I hope you all enjoy “Morning” and i am looking forward to making more work like this.
.
.
Orders start going out this week!
.
